vent","label":"Joseph Promoted in Egypt","slug":"event-111","score":10},{"id":"recZlsev4ThVh4o6I","type":"event","group":"event","label":"7 years of plenty","slug":"event-112","score":7},{"id":"rec85BvWuap3CDiMT","type":"event","group":"event","label":"7 years of famine","slug":"event-113","score":4}],"links":[{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"recIFusdNl6d8dj3L","label":"part of"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"recT5VXFTSilSlzVX","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"rechuDYJoK32gmrME","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"recNkoJz33pFlgcn2","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"recQvsOFh0nowQ1gD","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"reco82mzy0XTzaOgv","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"rec1YbscOE9IyJ5ey","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"recEtv9ql7Hh4XAW4","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"rec1RMZhQrrzq5oHJ","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"recK0feE032FY9Hxi","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"recqKt1B6fiiSKrK6","label":"event"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"recD7RqjeIpsJAoBc","label":"event"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"recZlsev4ThVh4o6I","label":"event"},{"source":"recIbu14OJJwJEe9q","target":"rec85BvWuap3CDiMT","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recvi5floLCygtJxP","ref":"Gen.41.1","text":"And it came to pass at the end of two full years, that Pharaoh dreamed: and, behold, he stood by the river.","year":-1715},{"id":"recWlI0L0H8NS9QQ8","ref":"Gen.41.2","text":"And, behold, there came up out of the river seven well favoured kine and fatfleshed; and they fed in a meadow.","year":-1715},{"id":"recDYR9QIm5ltKypo","ref":"Gen.41.3","text":"And, behold, seven other kine came up after them out of the river, ill favoured and leanfleshed; and stood by the other kine upon the brink of the river.","year":-1715},{"id":"rec6YCa3wNkmGHeRx","ref":"Gen.41.4","text":"And the ill favoured and leanfleshed kine did eat up the seven well favoured and fat kine. So Pharaoh awoke.","year":-1715},{"id":"recNyS6zW3Qd0uCJk","ref":"Gen.41.5","text":"And he slept and dreamed the second time: and, behold, seven ears of corn came up upon one stalk, rank and good.","year":-1715},{"id":"recmKGJDhV3DpDY2t","ref":"Gen.41.6","text":"And, behold, seven thin ears and blasted with the east wind sprung up after them.","year":-1715},{"id":"rec8zYqjzwCYcFWCY","ref":"Gen.41.7","text":"And the seven thin ears devoured the seven rank and full ears. And Pharaoh awoke, and, behold, it was a dream.","year":-1715},{"id":"recvEFOm22CKDRG8V","ref":"Gen.41.8","text":"And it came to pass in the morning that his spirit was troubled; and he sent and called for all the magicians of Egypt, and all the wise men thereof: and Pharaoh told them his dream; but there was none that could interpret them unto Pharaoh.","year":-1715}]}
